Healthy			Features & Innovation			Normal velocity
Warning		Reliability & Investigations		Reduced risk, smaller changes
Depleted		Fixing Root Causes			Freeze (except P0/Security)
Key Principle
Error budgets are intended to be a collaborative tool, not a punishment. When the budget is gone, the team agrees in advance to pause and fix, rather than blaming, ensuring long-term reliability and sustainable development. 
 
